title: Kentix Alarmmanager Pro: Leakage Sensor
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/environment/kentix
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the state of a leakage sensor connected to the
 Kentix Alarmmanger Pro device.
 Up to 100 Kentix Multisensors are connectable to the
 Kentix Alarmmanager Pro device.
 The additional leakage sensor operates as a N/C contact.

 The status is OK, if the device is connected and reports
 no alarm.
 The status changes to CRIT, if the device is disconnected or reports
 an alarm.

item:
 The name of the sensor.

inventory:
 One service is created for each sensor.
